The paper introduces a novel conditioning scheme for flow-based generative models, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also applies the proposed method to image manipulation and 3D point cloud reconstruction, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of multi-modal data modeling, which is a topic that falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also mentions the use of segmentation maps and edge masks, which are topics related to natural language processing and computer vision (cs.CL).
